anually investigate whether it is possible to manipulate some text within response 3, to enable full exploitation of this issue.','GET <a href=\"59.64.78.37:3003/vulnerabilities/sqli/?id=1&Submit=Submit\" target=\"_black\">59.64.78.37:3003/vulnerabilities/sqli/?id=1&Submit=Submit</a>');
